## 🧠 Quick Summary

| Term | What it means |
|---|---|
| `requirements.txt` | Shopping list of libraries your project needs |
| `pip install -r requirements.txt` | Install everything on the list |
| `pip freeze > requirements.txt` | Auto-generate the list from what's installed |
| `==` | Locks to an exact version of a library |
| `.gitignore` | Tells git to ignore files like `venv/` |
